63ByteArray BitMatrixParser::ReadCodewords(const BitMatrix& image)
64{
65 ByteArray result(144);
66 int height = image.height();
67 int width = image.width();
68 for (int y = 0; y < height; y++) {
69 for (int x = 0; x < width; x++) {
70 int bit = BITNR[y][x];
71 if (bit >= 0 && image.get(x, y)) {
72 result[bit / 6] |= static_cast<uint8_t>(1 << (5 - (bit % 6)));
73 }
74 }
75 }
76 return result;
77}
